DIAGNOSTIC INTELLIGENCE SCHEMA v1

This is the exact structure your system must produce.

1️⃣ Executive Layer
executive_summary: {
  readiness_score: number,
  readiness_category: "Manual | Fragmented | Transitional | Structured",
  primary_bottleneck_id: string,
  secondary_bottleneck_id: string,
  growth_risk_level: "Low | Moderate | High | Critical",
  estimated_annual_impact_range: {
    min: number,
    max: number
  },
  narrative_summary: string,
  confidence_score: number
}

This drives the top section of your Diagnostic tab.

2️⃣ Bottleneck Objects (Core Engine)

Every bottleneck must follow this exact anatomy.

bottlenecks: [
  {
    id: "B1",
    title: string,
    severity: "Moderate | High | Critical",
    category: "Revenue | Operations | Governance | Compliance",
    pattern_strength: number,
    
    causal_chain: [
      "Trigger",
      "Immediate Effect",
      "Secondary Effect",
      "Compounding Effect",
      "Failure Outcome"
    ],

    stress_simulation: {
      growth_20_percent: string,
      growth_30_percent: string,
      founder_absence: string,
      system_failure: string
    },

    root_cause_hierarchy: {
      level_1_symptom: string,
      level_2_process_failure: string,
      level_3_architecture_failure: string,
      level_4_governance_failure: string
    },

    quantified_impact: {
      revenue_leakage_estimate: number,
      payroll_inflation_risk: number,
      time_waste_hours_per_week: number,
      growth_ceiling_percent: number
    },

    intervention_path: {
      short_term: string,
      mid_term: string,
      structural_redesign: string
    },

    supporting_questions: [
      {
        question_id: string,
        client_answer: string,
        ai_interpretation: string,
        structural_implication: string
      }
    ]
  }
]

Every bottleneck must include every layer.
No skipping.

3️⃣ Systemic Pattern Engine

This aggregates signals across answers.

systemic_patterns: [
  {
    pattern_name: string,
    severity: "Low | Moderate | High",
    signal_count: number,
    cross_departmental_presence: boolean,
    failure_cascade_potential: string,
    recurrence_probability: number
  }
]

This prevents shallow isolated insights.

